{{伊朗政治}}

'''2008年伊朗議會選舉'''的首輪選舉在3月14日舉行<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rferl.org/content/article/1077006.html | title=Iran: Politicians Concerned About New Election Date | publisher=Radio Free Europe | date=08-06-2007 | accessdate=2011-06-02 | author=Vahid Sepehri | language=en | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304214511/http://www.rferl.org/content/article/1077006.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，第二輪選舉則在4月25日舉行<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.angelfire.com/ma/maxcrc/elections.html | title=Electoral Calendar | publisher=angelfire.com | accessdate=2011-06-03 | language=en | archive-date=2017-10-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014123213/http://www.angelfire.com/ma/maxcrc/elections.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於「幾乎所有重要的」改革派候選人的參選資格被取消，忠於總統[[馬哈茂德·艾哈邁迪內賈德|馬哈茂德·艾哈邁迪內賈德]]的[[伊朗原则主义派|原则主义派]]被視為是選舉的贏家<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1722817,00.html#ixzz0iekLsih7 | title=What Iran's Poll Results Mean | publisher=Time | date=2008-03-16 | accessdate=2011-06-03 | author=Nahid Siamdoust | language=en | archive-date=2013-08-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826060557/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1722817,00.html#ixzz0iekLsih7 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

